## Opcija 3: Nginx Reverse Proxy + Apache CXF (ENTERPRISE)

```nginx
# /etc/nginx/conf.d/soap-rest-adapter.conf

upstream soap_backend {
    server legacy-soap-server:8080;
}

upstream rest_backend {
    server rest-api:3000;
}

server {
    listen 80;
    server_name api.example.com;

    # Novi REST clients pristupaju REST API-ju
    location /api/v2/ {
        proxy_pass http://rest_backend;
    }

    # Legacy SOAP clients (fallback na SOAP)
    location /soap/ {
        proxy_pass http://soap_backend;
    }

    # ADAPTER logika - konvertujem zahteve
    location /adapter/ {
        # Presledi XML→JSON zahteve
        proxy_pass http://soap_backend;

        # Custom headers za adapter
        proxy_set_header X-Transform-Mode "soap-to-rest";
    }
}
```

