## **Generičke Prečice za AWS Provider Bugs**

### 1. **Downgrade Provider (Stara verzija koja radi)**
```hcl
# versions.tf
terraform {
  required_providers {
    aws = {
      source  = "hashicorp/aws"
      version = "5.45.0"  # Verzija PRE bug-a
    }
  }
}
```

```bash
terraform init -upgrade
```

### 2. **Zaobići Bug sa `lifecycle` Ignore**
```hcl
resource "aws_s3_bucket" "example" {
  bucket = "my-bucket"

  lifecycle {
    # Ignoriši bug (ne pokušavaj promenu)
    ignore_changes = [
      acl,
      object_lock_configuration
    ]
  }
}
```

### 3. **local-exec Workaround (Zaobiđi Provider)**
```hcl
resource "aws_ec2_instance" "example" {
  # ... config koji ne radi u Terraform-u

  provisioner "local-exec" {
    command = <<EOF
      aws ec2 run-instances \
        --image-id ami-12345 \
        --instance-type t3.micro \
        --tag-specifications 'ResourceType=instance,Tags=[{Key=Name,Value=bugfix}]'
    EOF
  }
}
```

### 4. **Data Source Umesto Managed Resource**
```hcl
# Ako je CREATE/UPDATE broken, koristi data source + external tool

data "external" "workaround" {
  program = ["bash", "setup.sh"]

  query = {
    resource_id = aws_s3_bucket.example.id
  }
}
```

### 5. **Null Resource + Local Provisioner (Super Hack)**
```hcl
resource "null_resource" "workaround" {
  provisioner "local-exec" {
    command = "aws logs put-retention-policy --log-group-name ${aws_cloudwatch_log_group.app.name} --retention-in-days 7"
  }

  depends_on = [aws_cloudwatch_log_group.app]
}
```

### 6. **AWS CLI sa Shell Script (Direktno!)**
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# workaround.sh - radi ono što Terraform ne može

aws elbv2 modify-target-group \
  --target-group-arn arn:aws:elasticloadbalancing:... \
  --matcher HttpCode=200,301 \
  --health-check-enabled true
```

```hcl
resource "null_resource" "fix_alb" {
  provisioner "local-exec" {
    command = "bash ${path.module}/workaround.sh"
  }
}
```

